{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/ios-date/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"83a41433-7393-5660-988a-f34d4b133010","html":"<h2 id=\"utccordinated-universal-time\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#utccordinated-universal-time\" aria-label=\"utccordinated universal time permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UTC(Cordinated Universal Time)</h2>\n<p>협정 세계시라고 하는 단위인데, 국제적인 표준시간의 기준이라고 한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>국제 사회가 사용하는 과학적 시간의 표준</li>\n<li>기존 평균태양시인 그리니치 표준시(GMT)를 대체하여 사용 (영국 그리니치 천문대 시간 기준.)</li>\n<li>우리나라(한국)는 런던을 기준으로 + 9시간 (빠름)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"date-구조체의-이해\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#date-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4\" aria-label=\"date 구조체의 이해 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Date 구조체의 이해</h2>\n<p>스위프트에서 기본으로 제공해주는 날짜를 다루는 Date구조체 타입</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> now <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 생성시점의 날짜와 시간을 생성해서 (기준 시간으로부터) 초단위 기준값을 가지고 있음.</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>now<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 그냥 출력하면 항상 UTC기준의 시간으로 출력</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"초-분-시간\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B4%88-%EB%B6%84-%EC%8B%9C%EA%B0%84\" aria-label=\"초 분 시간 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>초, 분, 시간</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>60초(1분) * 60분(1시간) * 24시간 = 하루를 초기준으로</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>3600초</li>\n<li>3600초 * 24 = 86,400초 (하루)</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> yesterday <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> now <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">86400</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>yesterday<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nnow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">timeIntervalSince</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>yesterday<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 해당 시점으로부터 차이를 초로 (86,400초 차이)</span>\nnow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">distance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>to<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yesterday<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// 지금시점을 기준으로 그 시간까지의 거리를 초로</span>\nyesterday<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">distance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>to<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> now<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nnow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">advanced</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>by<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">86400</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>             <span class=\"token comment\">// 내일</span>\nnow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addingTimeInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3600</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nnow <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">86400</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"정의된-타임존\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98%EB%90%9C-%ED%83%80%EC%9E%84%EC%A1%B4\" aria-label=\"정의된 타임존 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정의된 타임존</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> localeName <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">TimeZone</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>knownTimeZoneIdentifiers<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>localeName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ntimeZone<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"날짜와-시간-다루기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%82%A0%EC%A7%9C%EC%99%80-%EC%8B%9C%EA%B0%84-%EB%8B%A4%EB%A3%A8%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"날짜와 시간 다루기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>날짜와 시간 다루기</h2>\n<p>Date/Calender/DateFormatter</p>\n<ul>\n<li>날짜를 제대로 다루려면?</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>달력을 다루는 calendar 구조체의 도움도 필요 (양력, 음력인지)</li>\n<li>문자열로 변형해주는 DateFormatter 클래스의 도움도 필요</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>기본적으로 지역설정/타임존의 영향이 있음.</em></p>\n<Br/>\n<h3 id=\"calendar-구조체의-이해\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#calendar-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4\" aria-label=\"calendar 구조체의 이해 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Calendar 구조체의 이해</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>스위프트에서 기본으로 제공해주는, 달력(Calendar) 구조체 타입</li>\n<li>“절대 시점(Date)“을 연대/연도/날짜/요일과 같은 “달력의 요소”로 변환을 돕는 객체</li>\n<li>그레고리력 (Gregorian calendar) - 양력(전세계표준 달력)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> calendar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> calendar1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>identifier<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gregorian<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 직접 생성하기 (이런 방식으로 잘 사용하지는 않음)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> calendar2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>autoupdatingCurrent        <span class=\"token comment\">// 유저가 선택한 달력 기준(세계적 서비스를 한다면)</span></code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>지역설정 → 나라(지역)마다 날짜와 시간을 표시하는 형식과 언어가 다름</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\">calendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>locale     <span class=\"token comment\">// 달력의 지역(영어/한국어)</span>\ncalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>timeZone   <span class=\"token comment\">// 타임존 ==> Asia/Seoul (UTC 시간관련 개념)</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//필요할 때 찾아서 사용하면 됨.</span>\ncalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>locale <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">locale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>identifier<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"ko KR\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"date의-년월일시분초를-확인하는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#date%EC%9D%98-%EB%85%84%EC%9B%94%EC%9D%BC%EC%8B%9C%EB%B6%84%EC%B4%88%EB%A5%BC-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"date의 년월일시분초를 확인하는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Date의 “년/월/일/시/분/초”를 확인하는 방법</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>날짜 - 년/월/일</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> now <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> year<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> calendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>year<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> from<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> now<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//메서드 불러와서 .찍어보면 관련 항목 들을 볼 수 있다.</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>Date는 Calendar(양력)의 도움을 받아야 여러가지로 활용가능</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>하나의 요소가 아닌 여러개의 데이터를 얻는 방법 (Date Component)</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> myCal <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myDateCom <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> myCal<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dateComponents</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>year<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>month<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>day<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> from<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> now<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nmyDateCom<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>year\nmyDateCom<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>month\nmyDateCome<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>day\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"열거형으로-요일을-만들고-오늘의-요일을-계산하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%B4%EA%B1%B0%ED%98%95%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B3%A0-%EC%98%A4%EB%8A%98%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%94%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EA%B3%84%EC%82%B0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"열거형으로 요일을 만들고 오늘의 요일을 계산하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>열거형으로 요일을 만들고, 오늘의 요일을 계산하기.</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">enum</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Weekday</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> sunday <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> monday<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> tuesday<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> wednesday<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> thursday<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> friday<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> saturday\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> today<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Weekday</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> weekday <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>weekday<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> from<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 요일을 나타내는 정수</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</spa